'''Al-Sinaa Sport club''' ({{lang-ar|نادي الصناعة الرياضي|lit=''Industry SC''}}) is a [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Sadr City|Thawra District]], East Districts of the [[Tigris River]], [[Baghdad]], ''Al-Sinaa'' is Arabic for Industry.

==Honours==
*'''[[Iraq FA Cup]]''': 1

::1984

