==Personal life==
Perez works for an Electrical Department in Gibraltar.<ref>{{cite news|title=Gibraltar v Poland: Starting XIs by professional occupation|url=http://i100.independent.co.uk/article/gibraltar-v-poland-starting-xis-by-professional-occupation--l13c2aPE4g|accessdate=9 September 2014|publisher=The Independent}}</ref>
