{{refimprove|date=June 2016}}

'''Stade Omar Benhaddad''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Kouba, Algeria|Kouba]], district of [[Algiers]], [[Algeria]].  It is currently used mostly for [[Association football|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[RC Kouba]].  The stadium holds 10,000<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://stadiumdb.com/stadiums/alg/stade_mohamed_benhaddad|title=Stade Mohamed-Benhaddad – StadiumDB.com|website=stadiumdb.com|language=en|access-date=2018-02-01}}</ref> people.

