{{Infobox football biography | name = Serge Tsmikeboki | image = | fullname = Serge Tsmikeboki | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1967|2|16}} | birth_place = [[Pointe-à-Pitre]], [[Guadeloupe]] | height = 1.63 m | position = Striker | currentclub = | clubnumber = | years1 = 1988&ndash;1989 | years2 = 1989&ndash;1991 | years3 = 1991&ndash;1992 | clubs1 = [[US Villecresnes|Villecresnes]] | clubs2 = [[Chamois Niortais F.C.|Chamois Niortais]] | clubs3 = [[US Melle|Melle]] | caps1 = ? | caps2 = 8 | caps3 = ? | goals1 = ? | goals2 = 0 | goals3 = ? }}
'''Serge Tsmikeboki''' (born February 16, 1967) is a former professional [[association football|footballer]] who played as a striker.
